    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a reliable daily driver, though it shows clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, a few small door dings, and some fading on the clear coat on the roof. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and wear on the driver's seat bolster. Mechanically, the car starts and runs well, but the suspension is beginning to feel a bit loose and there is a slow oil leak that will eventually need attention. It\u2019s a solid choice for someone looking for affordable transportation who doesn't mind a few cosmetic and minor mechanical imperfections.",
