    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive excellence, this vehicle remains in pristine, showroom condition. The exterior finish retains its deep, factory luster with absolutely no swirls, chips, or imperfections, having been meticulously garaged and hand-washed throughout its life. Inside, the cabin is indistinguishable from new; the premium upholstery remains firm and unmarked, the dashboard is free of any sun damage, and every electronic component functions with factory precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, boasting a documented full-service history and a drive that is as smooth and responsive as the day it rolled off the assembly line. This is a rare find for a discerning enthusiast who demands perfection and a turn-key experience.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
