    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Presented in exemplary condition, this vehicle represents the pinnacle of automotive preservation. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a standard of care that is rarely encountered. Mechanically uncompromising and aesthetically indistinguishable from its original showroom state, this motorcar offers a refined driving experience for the discerning collector or enthusiast. We invite you to inspect this outstanding example of engineering excellence.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
