    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "Hey there! You seriously have to see this car\u2014it\u2019s an absolute dream! I\u2019ve babied this beauty since day one, and it\u2019s still in that gorgeous, showroom-ready condition that\u2019s getting harder to find. It drives incredibly smooth and looks practically brand new inside and out. I'm honestly a little sad to see it go, but I know the next owner is going to absolutely love it. Drop me a message if you want to come by and take a look!",
      "price": 47500.0,
