      "timestep_posted": 19
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offered is an investment-grade E46 M3, featuring the legendary S54B32 power plant with its high-revving individual throttle bodies and dual-VANOS system in flawless operational order. This example boasts a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission paired with a factory limited-slip differential. The chassis integrity is superlative, with a fully documented subframe reinforcement and fresh bushings throughout the suspension geometry. Finished in depth-defying Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the exterior retains its factory luster with zero signs of oxidation or panel misalignment. Mechanically, the valve clearances have been recently shimmed to spec, and the cooling system has been proactively overhauled with OEM components. A true turn-key specimen for the discerning collector.",
